            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1655804462396-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, remove 20g <span class=\"text-purple\">[30g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[40g]</span> <strong>butter</strong> from the fridge to warm up for later</p><p>Zest your<strong> lemon[s] </strong>and cut into wedges</p><p>Chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped chives</strong> and <strong>lemon zest</strong> with your <strong>soured cream </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>soured cream & chive dip</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
