    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>salmon flakes </strong>to a medium bowl with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>soured cream & chive dip </strong>(you'll use the rest later) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cover the <strong>salmon mixture</strong> with <strong>cling film</strong> and put it in the fridge to set before serving – this is your <strong>salmon rillettes</strong></p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the salmon rillettes mix into individual ramekins</p>",
