      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>cucumber</strong> finely into discs</p><p>Add the <strong>cucumber discs</strong>, <strong>yellow mustard seeds</strong> and <strong>cider vinegar</strong> to a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Mix everything together and set aside – this is your <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong></p>",
